            </div>

            <!-- Rich Text Body -->
            <div class="prose max-w-none" x-show="lang === 'zh'">
                <h2>适合每天上午做的一套动作</h2>
<p>广告账户巡检不需要一开始就很复杂。对大多数出海团队来说，每天固定 15 分钟检查五件事，就能提前发现大部分问题。</p>
<h3>第一步：看余额能撑多久</h3>
<p>不要只记录余额数字，要按最近 24 小时消耗估算还能撑几小时。如果低于一个主要投放高峰周期，就应该提前补款。</p>
<h3>第二步：看消耗有没有异常</h3>
<p>消耗突然下降，可能是审核、限额、素材疲劳或支付问题。消耗突然升高，也要确认 CPA 是否同步恶化。</p>
<h3>第三步：看素材审核队列</h3>
<p>统计待审、拒审、通过三类状态。拒审素材要记录原因，不要让同类问题重复发生。</p>
<h3>第四步：看支付方式</h3>
<p>检查银行卡、虚拟卡、代理充值通道是否正常。支付失败往往会引发连锁反应。</p>
<h3>第五步：看权限变化</h3>
<p>确认关键账户管理员、投手、财务角色没有异常变化。权限问题一旦出现在紧急时刻，处理成本会很高。</p>
<blockquote>
<p>SOP 的价值不是让团队更忙，而是让风险出现得更早、更清楚。</p>
</blockquote>
            </div>
            <div class="prose max-w-none" x-show="lang === 'en'" x-cloak>
                <h2>A Simple Daily Routine</h2>
<p>Account inspection does not need to start complicated. For most global teams, five checks in 15 minutes can catch many risks early.</p>
<h3>Balance Duration</h3>
<p>Do not only record balance. Estimate how many hours it can support based on the last 24-hour spend.</p>
<h3>Spend Abnormality</h3>
<p>A sudden drop may signal review issues, limits, creative fatigue, or payment failure. A sudden rise requires CPA checking.</p>
<h3>Creative Review Queue</h3>
<p>Track pending, rejected, and approved creatives. Record rejection reasons to avoid repeating the same issue.</p>
<h3>Payment Method</h3>
<p>Check cards, virtual cards, and recharge channels. Payment failure can create a chain reaction.</p>
<h3>Permission Changes</h3>
<p>Confirm admin, media buyer, and finance permissions. Permission problems are expensive during emergencies.</p>
            </div>

